-- RHB hires Credit Suisse to advise on Malaysia's three-way bank merger-sources
-- By Ngui Yantoultra and Saeed Azhar
-- Mon Jul 14, 2014 03:55AM EDT
-- None



July 14 (Reuters) - RHB Capital <RHBC.KL> has hired Credit Suisse <CSGN.VX> to advise on Malaysia's three-way banking merger, people with direct knowledge of the matter told Reuters on Monday.

Last week, CIMB Group Holdings Bhd <CIMB.KL>, RHB Capital and Malaysia Building Society Bhd <MBSS.KL>> received regulatory approval to begin merger talks to create a mega Islamic bank. [ID:nL4N0PL09R]